ive.com/uploads/NECA-DG-OYERINDE.jpeg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Sustaining Current Reforms Will Birth Positive Business Environment  " href="../../../2024/03/24/sustaining-current-reforms-will-birth-positive-business-environment5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Sustaining Current Reforms Will Birth Positive Business Environment  </h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari" href="../../../2024/03/23/el-yakubs-inelegant-disquisition-on-yemi-cardoso-mele-kyari5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Kyari.jpeg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari" href="../../../2024/03/23/el-yakubs-inelegant-disquisition-on-yemi-cardoso-mele-kyari5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">El-Yakub’s Inelegant Disquisition on Yemi Cardoso, Mele Kyari</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="  SETTING GLOBAL STANDARDS FOR GENDER EQUALITY" href="../../../2024/03/23/setting-global-standards-for-gender-equality5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/CSW_Banner.png" class="jsx-554